# Metric Resource: Synonyms
<https://w3id.org/cq2onto/metric/Synonyms> a dqv:Metric ;

    dcterms:identifier "https://w3id.org/cq2onto/metric/Synonyms" ;
    dcterms:title "Exact match against WordNet synonym relations"@en ;
    rdfs:label "Synonyms: Exact match against WordNet synonym relations"^^xsd:string ;
    vivo:abbreviation "synonyms"^^xsd:string ;
    dcat:version "0.0.1"^^xsd:string ;
    ftr:status "Active"@en ;
    dcat:landingPage <https://w3id.org/cq2onto/metric/Synonyms> ;

    # Descriptive Content
    dcterms:description """
This metric evaluates whether the generated label, expanded with its WordNet synonyms, exactly matches any label in the gold-standard ontology.

**Calculation Process:**

1. Retrieve all synonyms of the generated label from WordNet, forming a generated-label set.
2. Compare every member of the generated-label set against every gold-standard label using exact (case-insensitive) match.
3. If at least one pair matches, the result is 1; otherwise the result is 0.

**Example:**

Generated_label: Wine

Generated_label_set: Wine, alcohol, vintage, red_wine, white_wine, dark_red, …

Gold_standard_label: red_wine

Result: Synonyms(Gold_standard_label, Generated_label_set) = 1

**What is being measured?**

This metric identifies semantically equivalent concepts expressed through different lexical forms by leveraging the synonym relation curated in WordNet (or a comparable lexical dictionary).
""" ;
    dcat:keyword "Ontology Concept Matching"@en ;
    dcat:keyword "Metric"@en ;
    dcat:keyword "Classes"@en ;
    dcat:keyword "WordNet"@en ;

    # Relationships and Provenance
    dpv:isApplicableFor <https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q184754> ;
    ftr:hasBenchmark <https://w3id.org/cq2onto/benchmark/ALL> ;
    sio:SIO_000234 <https://w3id.org/cq2onto/metric/Synonyms> ;
    ftr:supportedBy <https://w3id.org/cq2onto/> ;
    dqv:inDimension "Ontology Engineering"^^xsd:string ;

    # Provenance
    dcterms:creator <https://orcid.org/0009-0001-9475-8159> ;
    dcat:contactPoint <https://orcid.org/0009-0001-9475-8159> ;
    dcterms:publisher <https://oeg.fi.upm.es> ;
    dcterms:publisher <https://ror.org/03n6nwv02> ;
    dcterms:license <http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/> .

